{
  "stem": "27509.9",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But as you talk to me, would it be acceptable to you if I write my master's thesis on [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the philosophy of Zionism according to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said, acceptable, and that was it, And-- So when did you complete your master's?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Within one year-- I went straight to Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't-- I didn't have the search books here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to the Hebrew University, spent six weeks there, very intensive study, and researched the subject, came back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It took me-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] no, I can't remember now exactly how long.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And by the end of the year, submitted the master's, and it was sent away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One copy went to England, to Manchester.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One copy went to Israel, to the very men who supervised my research, with-- unbeknown to me, the Melbourne department was connected with him.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he knew me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the third one was assessed here And I had my master's.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I've published my autobiography.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yes, in the meantime, Melbourne invited me to come and teach in the Hebrew literature, their department.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At first, they-- at first, I had my doubts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But then I gave in, and I taught there for four years, from the age of 65 to 69.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then, when I published my book, my autobiography--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've taught from '80, '82, '83, '84, and '85.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
